ets","discover_catalog_description":"Save, organize, and share content for your creative project without jumping between platforms. Keep track of your assets so you can find what you need, when you need it.","favorite_content":"Favorite content","filter_and_sort":"Filter and sort","find_items_faster_with_advanced_filtering_and_sorting":"Find items faster with advanced filtering and sorting.","gather_your_favorited_and_licensed_content":"Gather your favorited and licensed content in one place","get_started_cta":"Get started","group_assets_that_belong_together":"Group assets that belong together in collections.","group_assets_together_in_collections":"Group assets together in Collections","group_items":"Group items","introducing_insights":"Introducing Insights","introducing_insights_description":"See what content is trending, as well as the popularity and predictive performance scores for individual assets based on your market and industry.","keep_track_of_it_all":"Keep track of it all","keep_track_of_what_youve_licensed_and_saved":"Keep track of what you've licensed and saved.","locate_items_faster_with_advanced_filtering_and_sorting":"Locate items faster with advanced filtering and sorting.","manage_your_content_in_one_place":"Manage your content in one place","maximize_how_you_organize":"Maximize how you organize","maximize_how_you_organize_description":"No more hours lost to searching and moving content. It’s all in one place. Plus, you can add images, video, or music tracks to collections.","meet_shutterstock_catalog":"Meet Shutterstock Catalog","organization":"Organization","organize_better_so_you_can_find_faster":"Organize better so you can find faster","organize_content":"Organize content","search_for_your_assets_and_sort_results":"Search for your assets and sort results alphabetically or by date. Filter by asset type, asset status or license status. The best part? You can share your Collections with anyone, anywhere.","share_to_collaborate_with_partners_or_te